⚙️ Process Workflow
The bot follows a systematic execution flow to ensure data integrity:

Initialization: The bot launches the target web portal and authenticates.

Data Extraction: It navigates to the attendance section and scrapes the required records.

Data Processing: The raw data is cleaned, filtered, and formatted according to specific requirements.

Reporting: Finally, the bot populates an Excel/CSV file and saves it to a designated local path.

💡 Key Features
Error Handling: Implemented Try-Catch blocks to handle web element loading timeouts and connection drops.

Scalability: Designed to handle variable amounts of data without manual intervention.

Efficiency: Reduced the time required to complete attendance tracking from minutes to seconds.

🚀 How to Run
Requirements: You must have UiPath Studio or UiPath Assistant installed.

Environment Setup: Ensure your environment credentials (if any) are securely managed in the UiPath Orchestrator or local Config files.
